c: 7
v: 53
t: "Hara hi…ìe habbii si wanaa battane mun …óen? √ëalnde battane (firo) mayre arata, yejjitunoo…ìe …óum …ìen ko adii wi'ay : \"Gom…óii Nulaa…ìe Joomi amen …ìen addii goonga. Hara tefoo…ìe no woodani men …ìe tefana men? Maa men ruttee [aduna] men golla ko wanaa ko men gollaaynoo?\" Gom…óii …ìe hayrinii wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe ; kon ko …ìe fefindotonoo majjiri…ìe"